<!DOCTYPE html >
<html >
<head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0,maximum-scale=1.0,user-scalable=0"/> 
	<meta content="yes" name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" /> 
	<meta content="black" name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" /> 
	<meta content="telephone=no" name="format-detection" />
	<title>助学金中心</title>
  <script src="../js/jquery.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/css.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/css2.css" />
</head>

<body>

<div class="MBcenter">

  <div class="header"><a href="javascript:history.go(-1);" class="return_ico"></a>赚取助学金秘籍</div>
  
  <div class="zhuxueMj">
    <div class="number">1</div>
    <div class="main">
      <p>资讯分享</p>
      <span>每天分享1篇资讯可以获得1元助学金；</span>
    </div>
    <div class="clear"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="zhuxueMj">
    <div class="number">2</div>
    <div class="main">
      <p>课程分享</p>
      <span>每隔4天分享1篇课程可以获得3元助学金；</span>
    </div>
    <div class="clear"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="zhuxueMj">
    <div class="number">3</div>
    <div class="main">
      <p>网站任务</p>
      <span>网站任务分享1篇可以获得2元助学金；</span>
    </div>
    <div class="clear"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="zhuxueMj">
    <div class="number" style="background:#be0000;">4</div>
    <div class="main">
      <span style="margin-top:0">分享出去的链接必须被点击才会计算“助学金”（你也可以自己点击）。</span>
    </div>
    <div class="clear"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="zhuxueMj-bz">
    <p>备注：</p>
    <span>同一篇资讯、课程或同样的内容重复分享只计算一次助学金，即分享之前没有分享过的内容才可获得助学金哦。<br/>分享资讯一天内最高获得1元“助学金”。<br/>分享课程四天内最高获得3元“助学金”。<br/>网站任务分享一天内最高获得2元“助学金”。</span>
  </div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
